snippet.title: Overwatch 2 | One-Punch Man Collaboration Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing a collaboration of heroic proportions. Prepare to suit up and come out swinging with four exclusive Legendary skins including Saitama - Doomfist, Genos - Genji, Mumen Rider - Soldier 76, and Terrible Tornado - Kiriko! The Overwatch 2 x One-Punch Man collab hits the Shop today, Mar 7!

©ONE, Yusuke Murata/SHUEISHA, Hero Association HQ
